# Intuition
While loop will be useful 🤔😀

# Approach
As Fibonacci series is defined by this relation `Xn = Xn-1 + Xn-2`
We need three variables in total a,b & c.

Fibonacci series starts with 0 and 1, Hence assiging those values to a & b and then `c = a + b`

need to handle yielding of 0 and 1 separately rest of the series will taken care by our `while` loop

# Complexity
- Time complexity:
$$O(1)$$

- Space complexity:
$$O(1)$$

![image.png](https://assets.leetcode.com/users/images/dbe33423-1b15-458a-8d91-e9af0f8079f1_1685774097.9031093.png)

# Code
```
/**
 * @return {Generator<number>}
 */
var fibGenerator = function* () {
  let a = 0;
  let b = 1;
  let c = 0;

  if (c === 0) {
    c = a + b;
    yield 0;
  }
  if (c === 1) {
    yield 1;
  }

  while (true) {
    c = a + b;
    a = b;
    b = c;
    yield c;
  }
};


```

