# Approach
When we find a water cell, we recurse through it and its water cell neighbors. For each cell, we accumulate the value and then set it to 0 so that it will not be counted again. We store and return the max value.

# Complexity
- Time complexity : O(m*n)
- Space complexity: O(1)

# Code
