# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
1. Base Condition is if current node is leaf we returns its cost.
2. we perform dfs.
3. while backtracking we add difference in cost arrived from both child and add max of both to current cost and returns.
4. final asnswer is `ans` where we stored differences sum which returned at `i=0`.

