if you see carefully ,for every subtree the cost of parent node will be shared equally to left  tree portion and right tree portion.so we just need to balance the cost of left subtree and right subtree.so we calculate the difference of left subtree and right subtree cost ,that many times we perfom increment operation on the shortage side.

