# Intuition 
we can have 2 possiblities for start values of original array. 
1. original array can start with 1
2. original array can start with zero

since every value of derived array is depends only only current value & next of original array, we can maintain 2 variables which stores current values original array at that index. 

and based on derived value of at that index , we can alter those 2 pointers. 
