Iterate the string from backwards
Ex  : 00103215

Inititally i points to the left most end '0' .
According to our condition if the character is '0' assign the value of pointer(Ex : l) to the index value.Here i = num.length()-1 (here length = 8-1 = 7),therefore l = num.length()-1.
continue the process
check the next character if it is '0' update the l value.
If the character is not zero exit the loop.
Now the value of l = 6
Return the substring from 0 to l.



