<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->
First Thought of solving this problem is to start from LHS of String but that will create difficulty to find index from where trailing zeros has started. 

So, Starting from RHS will make task easier. 

# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
 Start checking for character other than 0 from the right hand side of the String.
If character other  than 0 is found take substring from 0 to that index+1 and break the loop.

At last return the String.



